@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Create a quiz
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/quizzes/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "course_id": "your-course-id",
  "title": "Quiz 3 - Binary Trees",
  "scheduled_date": "2025-04-10T09:00:00",
  "duration_minutes": 30,
  "weight_percent": 5.0,
  "topics_covered": "Binary Trees, BST, Tree Traversal"
}

### Get upcoming quizzes
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/quizzes/upcoming?days=14
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
